{"title":"Bioinformatics Division, National Institute of Biotechnology (NIB)","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Bioinformatics Division, National Institute of Biotechnology (NIB)","image":"nib_traning.jpg","date":"2022-06-11","description":"Teaching Instructor","format":{"html":{"includes":{"in_header":"style.css","before_body":"cover.html"}}}},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\ndocument.write(`\n<!-- Background Image with Gradient Overlay and Slideshow -->\n<div id=\"intro-section\" style=\"position: relative; text-align: center;\">\n\n  <!-- Slideshow Background -->\n  <div class=\"slideshow-container\">\n    <div class=\"mySlides fade\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3), rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3)), url('../../files/img/teaching/Bioinformatics_for_Biotechnology_Research/nib_traning_1.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mySlides fade\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3), rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3)), url('../../files/img/teaching/Bioinformatics_for_Biotechnology_Research/nib_traning_2.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mySlides fade\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3), rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3)), url('../../files/img/teaching/Bioinformatics_for_Biotechnology_Research/nib_traning_3.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mySlides fade\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3), rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3)), url('../../files/img/teaching/Bioinformatics_for_Biotechnology_Research/nib_traning_4.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;\"></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Structured Program Details Below the Image -->\n  <div id=\"program-details\">\n\n    <h2>Program Outline & Learning Objectives</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li class=\"justify\">\n        This program will help participants understand the basics of Linux OS and its applications in bioinformatics workflows, learn Bash scripting for automating NGS workflows, use Biopython and R programming for NGS data analysis and processing, perform Next Generation Sequencing (NGS) data analysis techniques, and apply bioinformatics tools for sequence alignment and variant calling.\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>Training Format and Activities</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Interactive lectures and presentations</li>\n      <li>Hands-on exercises for Linux OS and scripting</li>\n      <li>Practical demonstrations using Biopython</li>\n      <li>NGS data analysis workflow discussions</li>\n      <li>Assignments for participants</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>Instructors</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>All Team members</li>\n      <li>Bioinformatics Division, National Institute of Biotechnology (NIB)</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>Program Schedule</h3>\n    <ul class=\"program-schedule\">\n      <li><span>Day 1: Introduction to Linux OS and its role in bioinformatics</span></li>\n      <li><span>Day 2: Bash scripting for automation and task management</span></li>\n      <li><span>Day 3: Python and Biopython for NGS data analysis</span></li>\n      <li><span>Day 4: NGS workflows and data interpretation</span></li>\n      <li><span>Day 5: Final project and hands-on NGS data analysis</span></li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>Duration & Location</h3>\n    <p>Duration: 5 days <br> National Institute of Biotechnology (NIB), Dhaka, Bangladesh</p>\n\n    <p>\n      <a href=\"https://nib.gov.bd\" class=\"btn btn-primary rounded-pill me-2\"\n         style=\"padding: 15px 30px; font-size: .8em; text-decoration: none;\">\n         Program Details\n      </a>\n    </p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n`);\n</script>\n\n<style>\n  /* Slideshow container */\n  .slideshow-container {\n    position: relative;\n    height: 100vh;\n    width: 100%;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n\n  /* Each slide */\n  .mySlides {\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    background-size: cover;\n    background-position: center;\n    opacity: 0;\n    transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out;\n  }\n\n  .mySlides:first-child { opacity: 1; }\n\n  /* PROGRAM DETAILS */\n  #program-details {\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n    color: #000000;\n    background-color: #ffffff !important;\n    width: 100%;\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding: 60px 40px;\n    font-size: 1.1em;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n  }\n\n  #program-details h2, #program-details h3 {\n    margin-top: 22px;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n    font-weight: 800;\n    text-align: center;\n    text-shadow: none !important;\n    box-shadow: none !important;\n  }\n\n  #program-details ul {\n    list-style: none;\n    padding: 0;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  #program-details li {\n    margin: 6px 0;\n    text-shadow: none !important;\n    box-shadow: none !important;\n  }\n\n  #program-details li.justify {\n    text-align: justify;\n    margin: 0 20px;\n  }\n\n  #program-details p {\n    font-size: 1.05em;\n    text-align: center;\n    max-width: 900px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    text-shadow: none !important;\n    box-shadow: none !important;\n  }\n\n  /* PROGRAM SCHEDULE — EXTRA TIGHT */\n  .program-schedule{\n    display:flex;\n    flex-direction:column;\n    align-items:center;\n    gap:2px;                 /* was 6px */\n    padding:0;\n    margin:0 auto;\n  }\n\n  .program-schedule li{\n    width:100%;\n    display:flex;\n    justify-content:center;\n    margin:0;                /* keep zero */\n    padding:0;               /* keep zero */\n  }\n\n  .program-schedule li span{\n    max-width:900px;\n    width:100%;\n    display:block;\n    text-align:center;\n    line-height:1.05;        /* was 1.25 */\n    margin:0;\n    padding:0;\n  }\n\n  /* BUTTON */\n  .btn {\n    padding: 10px 20px;\n    font-size: 1em;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n    display: inline-block;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    background-color: #007BFF;\n    color: white;\n    border-radius: 999px;\n    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n  }\n\n  .btn:hover { background-color: #0056b3; }\n</style>\n\n<script>\n  document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function () {\n    let slideIndex = 0;\n    const slides = document.querySelectorAll('#intro-section .mySlides');\n    if (!slides || slides.length === 0) return;\n\n    function showSlides() {\n      slides.forEach((s) => (s.style.opacity = '0'));\n      slideIndex = (slideIndex + 1) > slides.length ? 1 : (slideIndex + 1);\n      slides[slideIndex - 1].style.opacity = '1';\n      setTimeout(showSlides, 3000);\n    }\n\n    showSlides();\n  });\n</script>","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\ndocument.write(`\n<!-- Background Image with Gradient Overlay and Slideshow -->\n<div id=\"intro-section\" style=\"position: relative; text-align: center;\">\n\n  <!-- Slideshow Background -->\n  <div class=\"slideshow-container\">\n    <div class=\"mySlides fade\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3), rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3)), url('../../files/img/teaching/Bioinformatics_for_Biotechnology_Research/nib_traning_1.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mySlides fade\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3), rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3)), url('../../files/img/teaching/Bioinformatics_for_Biotechnology_Research/nib_traning_2.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mySlides fade\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3), rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3)), url('../../files/img/teaching/Bioinformatics_for_Biotechnology_Research/nib_traning_3.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mySlides fade\" style=\"background-image: linear-